             were indicted, for <rs id="t17830430-9-off38" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17830430-9-off38" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830430-9-off38" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
