            , were indicted, for that they afterwards, to wit, on the same day, <rs id="t17830430-9-off41" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17830430-9-off41" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830430-9-off41" type="offenceSubcategory" value="receiving"></interp>
