               <p>*** She was tried again on the third day and found guilty.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17830430-9-person189">
                  THOMAS
                   WARRICKSHALL
               <interp inst="t17830430-9-person189" type="surname" value="WARRICKSHALL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17830430-9-person189" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
